250
00:22:00,610 --> 00:22:04,490
He tries a new game.

251
00:22:04,490 --> 00:22:08,700
He is going to make his opponent tired.

252
00:22:08,700 --> 00:22:11,170
He moves slowly.

253
00:22:11,170 --> 00:22:15,669
Sometimes he only stands there.

254
00:22:15,669 --> 00:22:21,230
Foreman hit him with big, heavy punches.

255
00:22:21,230 --> 00:22:23,049
People call out.

256
