282
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:39,929
"You're very sick," the doctor said.

283
00:24:39,929 --> 00:24:44,049
"And you're not going to get well.

284
00:24:44,049 --> 00:24:53,539
It's not going to kill you, but you're going
to get tired very quickly every day You're

285
