292
00:25:37,950 --> 00:25:42,309
People are people.

293
00:25:42,309 --> 00:25:51,149
Ali is happy because he was one of the first
famous black Americans.

294
00:25:51,149 --> 00:25:57,019
And now Ali is working for peace in the world.

295
00:25:57,019 --> 00:26:00,149
He makes money with his famous name.

296
00:26:00,149 --> 00:26:06,529
He meets and talks with governments and other
